dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents parcels for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Washburn_Parcels_2014.gdb. [The tax parcel layer for Washburn County parcels is intended to represent parcels referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. Orthophoto evidence was used for conflicting or problematic descriptions. The polygons are created from the boundary linework.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [The purpose of the tax parcel layer is to provide reference for the current spatial and tabular information provided by the taxroll and legal descriptions.]
